(def\ (newInstance class dim . dims)
  #|($nm class . dimensions)
   |(type function)
   |
   |(syntax dimension (integer . dimensions)
   |
   |Returns a new array with the elements of <b>class</b> tipe and the specified <b>dimensions</b>.
